name: UnofficialTaftSchoolDiningMenu
0:
”Alexa, ask Taft Dining whats on the menu today”
”Alexa, ask Taft Dining whats for lunch”
”Alexa, ask Taft Dining whats for dinner tomorrow”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: taft dining
des:
Want to know what they are serving for breakfast, lunch or dinner at the Horace Dutton Taft Servery. Just ask Taft Dining!

You can get the menu for any meal (breakfast, lunch or dinner) for today, tomorrow, or any future date. Even yesterday and past dates.

This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by The Taft School. Any comments, questions, complaints and praise should be sent to the Skill developer.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
